Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Tyson Chandler?

Tyson Chandler is 43 years old.

Where was Tyson Chandler born?

Tyson Chandler was born in Hanford, California.

When was Tyson Chandler born?

Tyson Chandler was born on October 2, 1982.

How tall is Tyson Chandler?

Tyson Chandler is 7-0 (213 cm) tall.

How much did Tyson Chandler weigh when playing?

Tyson Chandler weighed 235 lbs (106 kg) when playing.

Is Tyson Chandler in the Hall of Fame?

Tyson Chandler is not in the Hall of Fame.

When was Tyson Chandler drafted?

Tyson Chandler was drafted by Los Angeles Clippers, 1st round (2nd pick, 2nd overall), 2001 NBA Draft.

What position did Tyson Chandler play?

Center and Power Forward.

When did Tyson Chandler retire?

Tyson Chandler last played in 2020.

What is Tyson Chandler's net worth?

Tyson Chandler made at least $189,930,046 playing professional basketball.

How much did Tyson Chandler make?

Tyson Chandler made $14,598,888 in 2015.

What did Tyson Chandler average?

Tyson Chandler averaged 8.2 points, 9.0 rebounds, and 0.8 assists per game.

How many rings does Tyson Chandler have?

Tyson Chandler won one championship.

What schools did Tyson Chandler attend?

Tyson Chandler attended Dominguez in Compton, California.

What are Tyson Chandler's nicknames?

TC is a nickname for Tyson Chandler.
